quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  5,46,"Mu buwufu bwabwe (Abayudaaya) twagoberezaako Isa Mutabani wa Mariam ng’akakasa ebyo ebyamukulembera ebiri mu Taurat, era yajja nga bulungamu, era ekyokubuulirira eri abo abatya Katonda"
  5,47,"Kale nno abantu benjiri bateekeddwa okulamuza ebyo Katonda byeyassa mu yo, omuntu yenna atalamuza ebyo Katonda byeyassa abo nno bo be bonoonyi"
  5,48,"Era twassa gyoli (Ggwe Muhammad) ekitabo, mu bulambulukufu nga kikakasa e bitabo byonna e byakikulembera era nga kye kibisukkulumye. Kale lamula wakati waabwe nga okozesa e byo Katonda byeyassa togezaako okugoberera okwagala kwa bwe obe nga oleka amazima agakujjidde, buli bamu mu mmwe twabawa amateeka n'enkola singa Katonda yayagala yaalibafudde ekibiina kimu naye yayagala okubakema olwebyo byeyabawa, kale nno muvuganye mu kukola e birungi, anti eri Katonda yeeri obuddo bwa mmwe mwenna, gyalibategeereza ebyo byemwayawukanamu"
  5,49,"Era lamula wakati waabwe ng’okozesa ebyo Katonda byeyassa, togobereranga okwagala kwa bwe era beegendereze baleme kukuggya ku bimu ku ebyo Katonda byeyassa gyoli, bwebaba nga bakoze e kyennyume kyekyo, manya nti mazima Katonda ayagala okubavunaana olw'ebimu ku byonoono byabwe, wabula nga bulijjo abantu abasinga obungi bonoonyi"
  5,50,Ennamula y’ebiseera byobutamanya gyebaagala okukozesa! ani ayinza okuwa okulamula okulungi okusinga okuva ewa Katonda eri abo abakozesa amagezi gaabwe mu butuufu